data.description: Welcome to this fabulously semi-remodeled home in the heart of Krum. It boasts a modern open floor plan that floods with natural light through the home. This property has been meticulously maintained and kept clean by the seller and the love and care definitely shows that. You'll fall in love with the suite like primary bedroom that offers for relaxation and plenty of room to make your own. Notice the oversized secondary bedrooms that offer for tons of creativity with space from bedroom to office to a workout room. Camp out under the stars in the large backyard around your fire pit.
